reviewText: My favorite way to energize or unwind!!! It can be done at anytime of the day and I feel amazing afterwards! The music is so awesome and make you move every time!  I always feel centered and reset! I highly recommend this DVD! Syena is the best!

Syena does a great job of calmly starting then building up speed and quietly ending. Very pleased. It takes a couple of times before picking up the routine which prevented me from getting tired of it quickly. good challenge.
This video has awesome energy that will get you energized. Very easy to learn and fun to do. I recommend for everyone, regardless of age of activity level!!
This is a great activity for children.  I purchased it to have activities with our grandsons and they loved it!
